Riak database will be used to implement shopping cart.

Riak is open source distributed NoSQL database that ensures scalability as well as reliability.
Riak ensures :
1. High availability
2. Scalability
3. Fault tolerance
4. Operational simplicity

Riak is content-agnostic database which allows you to store anything you want - from JSON, Images, Binary, HTML etc.Riak database is used 
many Retail & eCommerce - BestBuy, Betzold, ideel, Shopzilla etc.

